attachments.title: Fashion photographer Miles Aldridge shoots the cast of Game of Thrones for Time Magazine
attachments.text: This Monday _Game of Thrones_ returns to our screens for its penultimate series. _Time_ magazine has dedicated a whole issue to the most popular TV show in the world and commissioned British fashion photographer Miles Aldridge to shoot the stars for the cover.
attachments.fallback: It&#8217;s Nice That: Fashion photographer Miles Aldridge shoots the cast of Game of Thrones for Time Magazine

attachments.title: A Top Nike Designer Rebrands Game Of Thrones
attachments.text: George R.R. Martin paints pictures with words, but what happens when a Nike designer translates these words into actual pictures? Wonderfulness.
attachments.fallback: Co.Design: A Top Nike Designer Rebrands Game Of Thrones

attachments.title: Sigils of the Houses of Westeros
attachments.text: My interpretation of various House Sigils from George R.R. Martin’s A Song of Ice and Fire series of fantasy novels. Done as a passion project to keep my love affair with the series fresh while waiting for the next novel. One of these currently hangs in the Belfast production office of the HBO
